      "widgets_values": [
        "## Plugging this into a workflow: \n- Plug this in between your prompt and your positive clip text endoders using the 🟢 reroutes\n\n\n- 💡This works with any model and anyone's workflow. \n\n**Seed** \n\n- You can hook it up to yours or totally unplug it and let the node choose. \n\n\n---\n### Follow me on CivitAi [HERE](https://civitai.com/user/lonecatone23)\n\n### Instagram: [synth.studio.models](https://www.instagram.com/synth.studio.models/)\n\n### This represents many of hours of work. If you enjoy it, please 👍like, 💬 comment , and feel free to ⚡tip or **[Buy me a☕](https://ko-fi.com/lonecatone)**\n\n---\n\n## 将此节点接入工作流：\n- 使用 🟢  reroute 节点，将它插在你的 **prompt** 和 **positive clip text encoders** 之间\n- 💡 此节点兼容任何模型和任意人的工作流。\n\n**Seed（种子）**\n- 你可以连接到自己的种子节点，也可以完全断开，让节点自动选择。\n\n---\n### 在 Civitai 上关注我 [HERE](https://civitai.com/user/lonecatone23)\n### Instagram: [synth.studio.models](https://www.instagram.com/synth.studio.models/)\n### 这花费了我大量时间和精力。如果你喜欢，请 👍点赞、💬留言，也欢迎 ⚡打赏 或 **[请我喝杯☕](https://ko-fi.com/lonecatone)**"
