          "input_ue_unconnectable": {}
        }
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "## Florence Notes:\n\n\n### 💡 I'll typically run this once, cut & paste the prompt out of it, drop it into the prompt area, and edit accordingly. \n\n## settings\n- **Model** any of the *\"prompt_gen_base\"* models work. Size and version affect the outcome.\n- bf16 works just as well as FP16 and is the best balanced choice \n- **caption/ detailed_caption/ more_detailed_caption:** works best for natural language models (Flux, ZIT, Qwen)\n- **prompt_gen_tags:** Good for SDXL, *but...*\n- **⭐ prompt_gen_mixed_caption:** works extremely well for SDXL, ILLU, Pony, N00B as well as for Zit. (mixed reviews on Flux. tends to just double stuff up)\n\n---\n\n## Florence 笔记：\n### 💡 我通常只会运行一次，然后将生成的 prompt 剪切粘贴出来，放入提示词区域，再进行相应编辑。\n\n## 设置\n- **Model**：使用任意 *\"prompt_gen_base\"* 模型即可。模型大小和版本会影响生成效果。\n- bf16 的效果与 FP16 相当，是平衡性最好的选择。\n- **caption / detailed_caption / more_detailed_caption**：最适合自然语言模型（Flux、ZIT、Qwen）。\n- **prompt_gen_tags**：适合 SDXL，*但……*\n- **⭐ prompt_gen_mixed_caption**：对 SDXL、ILLU、Pony、N00B 以及 Zit 效果极佳。（Flux 评价不一，容易出现内容重复。）\n"
      ],
      "color": "#222",
      "bgcolor": "#000"
    },
